  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-d659aa9d-a9ff-4046-8f9b-106cadd76e8c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a747b353-a4b2-48f9-a6e7-bacb1916d98d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f89d57a9-e0bc-4fce-b635-655276ab1c93\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>갤러리 홍보용 인쇄물 : 엽서</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-02c949e8-7e0b-4f00-b65f-6568cbe15b96\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-78fb9b82-b83f-4ee6-8b4c-59b8c67f0d49\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-64281c1b-e4da-41d6-a6f1-8d491ac68ce7\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">현재 코로나로 인해 미술 전시시장도 많이 위축되고 전시회도 일정이 취소되거나 미뤄지는 등 많은 고통을 겪고 있습니다. 2023년에는 더욱 갤러리 시장이 활성화되어 전시나 기타 여러가지 홍보가 많이 이루어졌으면 하는 바램이 있습니다. 먼저 미술관계자 여러분들에게  많은 응원과 격려의 말씀을 드립니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-8fef65bf-2061-47ed-86ce-8f91f668b671\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-943ea6ad-067b-459d-a87a-b68d2ed2f9c2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b1145faa-e5e8-4e1a-92d7-dc663c0c60ad\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8486d287-cb86-461f-a370-1742ce010bfd\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222934239556\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/222934239556</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>  <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1e05cc54-6b3c-4da6-a9f0-805f04f6b131\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ad950528-0329-4003-9642-4fdb018b046f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8afc41e3-5498-49d2-b7e1-fbfe161d93aa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d8f05ce7-97ce-485d-96de-1df1605a70cd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:474px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d8f05ce7-97ce-485d-96de-1df1605a70cd\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjNfMjQw/MDAxNjY5MTc0MzMzNzky.ljYxzRwNLJiX0BM7cfJu7WvhyokqlI8LBEEnptpFJwIg.cglepMefUQIuv5YSSdQgxCufJennZu3D5un0GmG_GVog.PNG.cookthedesign/01_%EA%B0%A4%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC_%EC%97%BD%EC%84%9C_1.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"474\", \"originalHeight\" : \"533\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjNfMjQw/MDAxNjY5MTc0MzMzNzky.ljYxzRwNLJiX0BM7cfJu7WvhyokqlI8LBEEnptpFJwIg.cglepMefUQIuv5YSSdQgxCufJennZu3D5un0GmG_GVog.PNG.cookthedesign/01_%EA%B0%A4%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC_%EC%97%BD%EC%84%9C_1.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6b1209cd-4d0b-4473-983a-8a02800b7869\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-84bc936e-ab7e-4cbe-a494-3bc58876f2ab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dc222aac-9ba4-42ee-968f-0dde807d5c20\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">디자인 비용은 기본 앞뒤로 2page 작업비로 11,000원(부가세 포함)입니다. 다만 이 작업은 다음과 같은 원하는 자료가 있을 경우이며 기타 템플릿을 벗어나는 디자인인 경우는 별도의 비용이 청구될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f2118265-f51c-49c4-86e0-104a3d2b3327\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9675ee03-4b05-4f71-beef-007da5759b25\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9b3410b9-6efd-425f-8a2a-c84d18765b87\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9a5fdce1-740c-42c2-b787-9405a9ced6f3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5c6147f3-aeac-41e5-83cd-561ec568e64c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-5c6147f3-aeac-41e5-83cd-561ec568e64c\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjNfMTEz/MDAxNjY5MTc1NTI3MjUw.J18OK05q2e4ezY-2wBesWJX102UMfAMieEOlAzk50PMg.mNov5axWjayQ58IfG-jXov6cf7J51kTZer_JTKyIva8g.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3535\", \"originalHeight\" : \"238\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjNfMTEz/MDAxNjY5MTc1NTI3MjUw.J18OK05q2e4ezY-2wBesWJX102UMfAMieEOlAzk50PMg.mNov5axWjayQ58IfG-jXov6cf7J51kTZer_JTKyIva8g.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c8d2ea71-b503-4a9d-b6bd-5bc42db81ea4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7b5e2b6c-dd29-4809-a053-6aad50b03da3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9873312b-b25b-4c42-8197-55156155334e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9c4305ac-fb55-4ff1-8b91-bbcce5cde211\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>기본 템플릿 형태 : 11,000원</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6c3b9a5e-94fc-462a-a9e5-23c23578d8be\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5a8249dd-2b49-41ad-9360-d0a0e18fbbc6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 앞면은 작품사진을 풀(full)로 채워 디자인을 하고 필요하면 작품명이나 작가성명 정도를 넣어 디자인 할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ae6a5023-17bb-48c1-81c5-3be4972b934c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b24f2e7d-2499-4236-b3cf-f11206d6cd8e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 디자인은 내용을 크게 해치지않는 범위에서 작업이 이루어집니다. 다만 조심해야 할것은 작품이미지의 해상도입니다. 최대한 좋은 이미지 해상도의 사진이어야 인쇄시 어둡거나 기타 조도, 색도를 느낄 수 있습니다. 간혹 작품의 색상과 인쇄물이 달라 클레임을 요청하는 경우도 있습니다. 이 부분은 전달된 이미지의 해상도나 기타 인쇄방법에 따라 달라질 수 있습니다. 좋은 작품의 해상도의 엽서를 원하실 경우는 반드시 문의를 주시기 바랍니다. 인쇄감리를 통해 최대한 맞춰 진행할 수 있습니다. 이렇게 작업이 진행될 경우 비용과 납기는 추가될 수 있음을 이해해 주십시요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-98b940b5-9e6e-4bdb-b55f-97c37d3eb2cd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:591px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-98b940b5-9e6e-4bdb-b55f-97c37d3eb2cd\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjNfOTIg/MDAxNjY5MTc1MzY2Mjk0.Hi38-mImHTORLES6q7b-LsmIk3dA6GP-l93sbNn-SMMg.AiIlKgjZqJvaR1-gRwhFAsN3at199XbJ5aPqy6wUgycg.PNG.cookthedesign/01_%EA%B0%A4%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC_%EC%97%BD%EC%84%9C_1.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"591\", \"originalHeight\" : \"474\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjNfOTIg/MDAxNjY5MTc1MzY2Mjk0.Hi38-mImHTORLES6q7b-LsmIk3dA6GP-l93sbNn-SMMg.AiIlKgjZqJvaR1-gRwhFAsN3at199XbJ5aPqy6wUgycg.PNG.cookthedesign/01_%EA%B0%A4%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC_%EC%97%BD%EC%84%9C_1.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-720acc76-64e3-4a9c-b53e-3b8149652c97\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:592px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='